@startuml
title 2. User & Payout Destination Management Flow

actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "Your Website" as Website
participant "Your Backend" as Backend
database "Your Database" as DB

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

Admin -> Website: Navigates to "Add Customer" page
Admin -> Website: Fills in customer details and 
payout information (Bank Account or PayID)
Website -> Backend: **POST /api/customers**
activate Backend

Backend -> Backend: Validate input data
Backend -> DB: Securely store customer and payout info 
 (Encrypt sensitive data)
activate DB
DB --> Backend: Confirm storage
deactivate DB

Backend --> Website: HTTP 201 Created
deactivate Backend

Website --> Admin: Show "Customer successfully created"

@enduml
